name: Oh No Its A Virus
description:
Wait for the cutscene to end and then hover your mouse over the virus to delete it

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You get bored of all your friends playing together but being left out because you do not have Minecraft. So you thought of a way to get it. surely searching it up online for free is a good idea.... or was it.

-- This was made for the winter jam 2022 --
